data.description: Single story Kyle Paul home built in 2018 located in highly desired Potosi Prairie Addition. 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and 2 car garage - giving you 1,730 sq. ft. of spacious elegance, beautiful floors throughout, and open kitchen with granite counters and stainless steel appliances. Vaulted ceilings in the living room with a stone fireplace as the center piece and a built in bookshelf, tons of natural light and lots of wall space. Large master bedroom with vaulted ceilings and an on-suite bathroom with separate shower and bathtub. Large closets. Split floor plan with 2 more good sized bedrooms. The open concept is perfect for entertaining and the back doors lead out to a great backyard that is perfect for entertaining. Large backyard is fully fenced with a covered patio. Storage shed stay with the property. Separate fenced area that can be used for a dog run, chickens or even goats. All of this is situated on a large lot in a convenient, friendly neighborhood with outstanding schools
